{"type": "article", "id": 3863, "title": "几何造型戒指", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-26T07:30:39Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233042F6JQR2rZOBYleEqx.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t纽约工业设计师 Evan Dewhirst 创办了一个个人工作室 Objcts ，日前他的工作室推出了一系列几何造型的戒指，Evan Dewhirst 将其命名为「轮廓」（ Silhouette ）。这一系列男女皆宜的戒指提供圆形、正方形、三角形以及六边形 4 种款式。在 Evan Dewhirst 看来，最酷的事情是这些戒指都可以通过 3D 打印技术实现，这就意味着可以有多种制作材质可选，并且让自定义尺寸变得更加容易。定价 47 美元，<a href=\"http://www.shopobjcts.com/shop-1\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233040uLSh8gsbjXz9xBdl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7421875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060523304063g420R5MjHzwTut.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7421875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233040PGb6z3OysKJED1e0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.384375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233041OFIi8DheYMJ9Qz4U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7421875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}